data.description: Great Floor Plan with main level masters suite! Features 3BR, 2.5BA; open kitchen with an island, birch cabinets, and gas range overlook the vaulted ceilings in the great room. Flexible loft space is perfect for an office or entertainment overlooks 2 story great room! Unfinished storage room on 2nd level perfect for storage! Backyard has fenced in vinyl privacy fence with an upgraded insulated shed!  Refrigerator;washer/dryer;Security System will come with the home at no extra expense!  Great value in this home! Convenient location to shopping, hospitals, highways! Ask about preferred lender's credit of 2k that can be used for closing costs.
